QuestionPage.AssessmentDetails.Title=SDM\u00AE Reunification Assessment
Cluster.Title.FinalRisk=Risk
RiskFactors.InstructionText=<p style="font-family:tahoma;font-size:11px;color:#4e4e4e;">Enter risk factors regarding the children in the household.</p>
Question.Label.InitialCPSRiskLevel=R1. Risk level on most recent referral (not the reunification risk level or risk reassessment)
Question.Help.InitialCPSRiskLevel=The initial risk level for the investigation is used to score this item. Select 'no initial risk level' if there is no risk assessment for this family.
Question.Label.Substantiations=R2. Has there been a new substantiation since the initial risk assessment or last reunification reassessment?
Question.Help.Substantiations=Answer 'YES' if complaints have been received since the last risk assessment or reassessment.
Question.Label.CasePlanGoalsProgress=R3. Progress toward Case Plan Goal
Question.Help.CasePlanGoalsProgress=Rate each caregiver's progress with the current case plan. Does Observation demonstrate the caregiver's application of learned skills in interactions between child/caregiver, caregiver to caregiver, caregiver to other significant adult, self-care, home maintenance, financial management, or demonstration of skills toward reaching the behavioral objectives agreed upon in the case plan?  Or is the caregiver  minimally participating in services OR has made progress but is not fully complying with the objectives in the case plan? Or does the caregiver refuse services, sporadically follows the case plan, or has not demonstrated the necessary skills due to a failure or inability to participate? Choose the most appropriate response.